title: 872. Big Week 6 Games, 8 Things We Learned, Standout Rookies & Favorite Performances
itunes:title: 872. Big Week 6 Games, 8 Things We Learned, Standout Rookies & Favorite Performances
description:
Daniel Jeremiah, Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis look back at the weekend and all the action from Week 6 of the NFL season. The guys start by breaking down the big 3 games from Sunday. After, the group hit on the 8 things they learned from Week 6. Following that, the guys each give a standout rookie and also their favorite performance. Then, the trio focus on how the Jets defensive line shut down the Packers.
